ZH: 我在地图上看到了一个大洋。
EN: I saw a big ocean on the map.

ZH: 海龟在大洋里游泳。
EN: The sea turtle is swimming in the ocean.

ZH: 我梦想着能环游世界各大洋。
EN: I dream of sailing across all the oceans of the world.

ZH: 他的家乡在大洋对面。
EN: His hometown is across the ocean.

ZH: 大洋深处有许多神秘生物。
EN: There are many mysterious creatures in the depths of the ocean.

ZH: 这艘船将穿梭在各个洋上。
EN: This ship will sail across various oceans.

ZH: 我们来到了大西洋的彼岸。
EN: We arrived at the other side of the Atlantic Ocean.

ZH: 我在沙滩边独自观赏着大洋的美景。
EN: I stood alone on the beach, admiring the beauty of the ocean.

ZH: 那些渔民依靠大洋为生。
EN: Those fishermen depend on the ocean for their livelihood.

ZH: 大洋里有很多不同种类的鱼。
EN: There are many different types of fish in the ocean.

ZH: 我想在大洋深处潜水探险。
EN: I want to go diving to explore the depths of the ocean.

ZH: 大洋永远是我最向往的地方。
EN: The ocean will always be my favorite place.

ZH: 我们将横渡太平洋到达目的地。
EN: We will cross the Pacific Ocean to reach our destination.

ZH: 每当我看到大洋我就感到无比宁静。
EN: I feel incredibly tranquil whenever I see the ocean.

ZH: 大洋的气候变化无常，需要注意安全。
EN: The climate of the ocean is unpredictable, so we need to be cautious.

ZH: 我想在大洋边搭建一个小木屋。
EN: I want to build a small cabin by the ocean.

ZH: 大西洋和太平洋分别是两大洋之一。
EN: The Atlantic and Pacific Oceans are two of the major oceans.

ZH: 我们将会横渡七大洋。
EN: We will cross all seven oceans.

ZH: 大洋上的风暴让人心惊胆颤。
EN: Storms on the ocean are terrifying.

ZH: 大洋之间有着无法桥接的距离。
EN: There is an unbridgeable distance between the oceans.
